Class State<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • State<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type for identifier for the City of a State, e.g E is of type Integer; City can be referred to as 1, 2, etc.

    public class State<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores the current City that AStarSearch is up to, as well as information about the search space such as total cost of the paths taken to this State and the remaining trips to be found by AStarSearch.
    Author:
    Zac Hamid - z5059915
